text:
Listen to Vince Staples’ New Song “BagBak” Released ahead of “The Life Aquatic Tour” with Kilo Kish Vince Staples Photo by James W. Mataitis Bailey 
Vince Staples has released a new single, “BagBak.” It arrives ahead of “ The Life Aquatic Tour ” (with Kilo Kish), which kicks off later this month in California. Hear the track below via Apple Music.
